- 删除 contracts 中无调用者的 Core MessageRef 转换与依赖。
- 删除 executor 未使用的 agent-types 直接依赖并更新 lockfile。
- 固化剩余 Product caller 与 legacy boundary 的最终 owner、调用链和 S5 原子切换前置。
- 明确本提交仅为 W2 activation component，待 W7 target caller 合入后完成旧 crate 与 serde bridge 删除。
---
 Cargo.lock                                        |  2 --
 crates/agentdash-contracts/Cargo.toml             |  1 -
 crates/agentdash-contracts/src/runtime/session.rs | 10 ----------
 crates/agentdash-executor/Cargo.toml              |  1 -
 4 files changed, 14 deletions(-)

diff --git a/Cargo.lock b/Cargo.lock
index f635ce9c..30362c84 100644
--- a/Cargo.lock
+++ b/Cargo.lock
@@ -601,7 +601,6 @@ name = "agentdash-contracts"
 version = "0.1.0"
 dependencies = [
  "agentdash-agent-protocol",
- "agentdash-agent-types",
  "agentdash-domain",
  "agentdash-spi",
  "chrono",
@@ -639,7 +638,6 @@ dependencies = [
 name = "agentdash-executor"
 version = "0.1.0"
